flowchart LR
  A[Raw imagery<br/>train/val root] --> B[Tiling<br/>tiles_manifest.json]
  B --> C[Split<br/>split.json]
  C --> D[Training + validation<br/>metrics.json + train_manifest.json]
  D --> E[Gate A<br/>validation KPIs]
  E --> F[MLflow candidate<br/>registry_result.json]
  F --> G[Golden full-scene evaluation<br/>sliding-window inference]
  G --> H[Gate B<br/>golden KPIs]
  H --> I[MLflow production<br/>promoted model version]
  D -. metrics/artifacts/model .-> M[MLflow Tracking]
  M -. registered model .-> F
